<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE reference PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Reference//EN" "reference.dtd">
<reference id="api_playeffect1">
    <title><ph keyref="playEffect1"/>[1/3]</title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">播放指定的本地或在线音效文件。</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="playEffect1" />
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody><section id="prototype">
        <p conref="../conref/conref_rtc_api.dita#apidef/playEffect1"/>
    </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <dl outputclass="deprecated">
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>弃用：</dt>
                    <dd>该方法自 v2.3.0 起废弃，请改用 <xref keyref="playEffect3"/>[3/3] 方法。</dd>
                </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>你可以多次调用该方法，传入不同的 <parmname>soundID</parmname> 和 <parmname>filePath</parmname>，同时播放多个音效文件。为获得最佳用户体验，Agora 推荐同时播放的音效文件不超过 3 个。</p>
            <p>音效文件播放结束后，SDK 会触发 <apiname keyref="onAudioEffectFinished"/> 回调。</p>
            <note outputclass="note">该方法需要在加入频道后调用。</note>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>参数</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry conkeyref="playEffect3/soundid">
                    <pt/>
                    <pd/>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>filePath</pt>
                    <pd>
                        <p conkeyref="playEffect3/filepath"/>
                    </pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry conkeyref="playEffect3/loopcount">
                    <pt></pt>
                    <pd></pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry conkeyref="playEffect3/pitch">
                    <pt></pt>
                    <pd></pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry conkeyref="playEffect3/pan">
                    <pt></pt>
                    <pd></pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry conkeyref="playEffect3/gain">
                    <pt></pt>
                    <pd></pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values" conkeyref="playEffect3/return_values"/>
    </refbody>
</reference>
